    <title>Refugees contributor: Simon McMahon</title>
    <description>Simon McMahon is a Research Fellow at the Centre for Trust, Peace and Social Relations at Coventry University. He is co-author of ‘Unravelling Europe’s Migration Crisis’ (Policy Press, 2017) and author of ‘Immigration and Citizenship in an Enlarged European Union’ (Palgrave, 2015). Simon’s email is simon.mcmahon@coventry.ac.uk and is on Twitter as @si_mcmahon.
</description>
